- How To Open .txt Files : 
	leafpad <fileName.txt>
	nano <fileName.txt>
	vim <fileName.txt>
- How To Install A Tool : 
	sudo apt install <toolName> -y
	' sudo : super user do '
	' apt package manager '
	' -y for yes condition ' 
- How To Change Directory : 
	cd <directoryName> 
- How To Reverse Directory : 
	cd ..
- How To Go Home Directory :
	cd 
- How To Create Directory : 
	mkdir <directoryName>
- How To Delete Directory :
	rm -r <directoryName>
	' rm = remove '
	' -r = recursion ( remove all files inside ) '
- How To Create A File :
	touch <fileName.fileExtention>
- How To Exit VIM : 
	:wq!


